Name: Zombie Season
About the game: Zombie Season has hit Pine City, are you the rookie cop that has the guts to save it? Experience an Open World and try your hand at survival in the plague ridden city. Get locked and loaded, jump in your police car and roam the streets to exterminate the zombie presence. Fly helicopters, find new weapons, and do what you can to make it out alive. Can your survive Zombie Season? Recent Changes: Open World Update - Free Roam and Drive cars Open World Update - Fly Helicopters AKs, Water Ski, Hat and Explosives Roadmap This next month: Open World Improvement Long Term: Steam Cloud Saves 10+ guns total 10 enemy types Greater enemy variation More scattered usable items
